### Frontend Polling Optimization

#### [MODIFY] [NotificationBell.tsx](file:///c:/Users/LENOVO/Downloads/CreaSearch-main/CreaSearch-main/frontend/src/components/NotificationBell.tsx)

Addresses: Excessive Repeated Calls to Notification Count, Continuous Background Fetch Pattern

- Increase poll interval from `30000ms` to `60000ms` (30s → 60s)
- Add `document.visibilityState` check — skip fetching when tab is hidden
- Add a short debounce: if the last fetch was < 5s ago, skip

#### [MODIFY] [api.ts](file:///c:/Users/LENOVO/Downloads/CreaSearch-main/CreaSearch-main/frontend/src/lib/api.ts)

Addresses: Profile Deletion Followed by Repeated 404 Fetches

- In `profileApi.getMyProfile()`, after receiving a 404, set a local flag to avoid repeat calls for the same userId within a short window (prevents the tight 404 loop)

